te-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b><a href=\"ConceptMap-CMVFReligion.html\">VF_Religion</a></b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/3.1.0/CodeSystem-v3-ReligiousAffiliation.html#v3-ReligiousAffiliation-1001\">1001</a></td><td>Adventist</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/3.1.0/CodeSystem-v3-ReligiousAffiliation.html#v3-ReligiousAffiliation-1002\">1002</a></td><td>African Religions</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/3.1.0/CodeSystem-v3-ReligiousAffiliation.html#v3-ReligiousAffiliation-1003\">1003</a></td><td>Afro-Caribbean Religions</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/3.1.0/CodeSystem-v3-ReligiousAffiliation.html#v3-ReligiousAffiliation-1004\">1004</a></td><td>Agnosticism</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/3.1.0/CodeSystem-v3-ReligiousAffiliation.html#v3-ReligiousAffiliation-1005\">1005</a></td><td>Anglican</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/3.1.0/CodeSystem-v3-ReligiousAffiliation.html#v3-ReligiousAffiliation-1006\">1006</a></td><td>Animism</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/3.1.0/CodeSystem-v3-ReligiousAffiliation.html#v3-ReligiousAffiliation-1061\">1061</a></td><td>Assembly of God</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/3.1.0/CodeSystem-v3-ReligiousAffiliation.html#v3-ReligiousAffiliation-1007\">1007</a></td><td>Atheism</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/3.1.0/CodeSystem-v3-ReligiousAffiliation.html#v3-ReligiousAffiliation-1008\">1008</a></td><td>Babi &amp; Baha'I faiths</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/3.1.0/CodeSystem-v3-ReligiousAffiliation.html#v3-ReligiousAffiliation-1009\">1009</a></td><td>Baptist</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/3.1.0/CodeSystem-v3-ReligiousAffiliation.html#v3-ReligiousAffiliation-1010\">1010</a></td><td>Bon</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/3.1.0/CodeSystem-v3-ReligiousAffiliation.html#v3-ReligiousAffiliation-1062\">1062</a></td><td>Brethren</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/3.1.0/CodeSystem-v3-ReligiousAffiliation.html#v3-ReligiousAffiliation-1011\">1011</a></td><td>Cao Dai</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/3.1.0/CodeSystem-v3-ReligiousAffiliation.html#v3-ReligiousAffiliation-1012\">1012</a></td><td>Celticism</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/3.1.0/CodeSystem-v3-ReligiousAffiliation.html#v3-ReligiousAffiliation-1013\">1013</a></td><td>Christian (non-Catholic, non-specific)</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/3.1.0/CodeSystem-v3-ReligiousAffiliation.html#v3-ReligiousAffiliation-1063\">1063</a></td><td>Christian Scientist</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/3.1.0/CodeSystem-v3-ReligiousAffiliation.html#v3-ReligiousAffiliation-1064\">1064</a></td><td>Church of Christ</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/3.1.0/CodeSystem-v3-ReligiousAffiliation.html#v3-ReligiousAffiliation-1065\">1065</a></td><td>Church of God</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/3.1.0/CodeSystem-v3-ReligiousAffiliation.html#v3-ReligiousAffiliation-1014\">1014</a></td><td>Confucianism</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/3.1.0/CodeSystem-v3-ReligiousAffiliation.html#v3-ReligiousAffiliation-1066\">1066</a></td><td>Congregational</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/3.1.0/CodeSystem-v3-ReligiousAffiliation.html#v3-ReligiousAffiliation-1015\">1015</a></td><td>Cyberculture Religions</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/3.1.0/CodeSystem-v3-ReligiousAffiliation.html#v3-ReligiousAffiliation-1067\">1067</a></td><td>Disciples of Christ</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/3.1.0/CodeSystem-v3-ReligiousAffiliation.html#v3-ReligiousAffiliation-1016\">1016</a></td><td>Divination</td><td/></tr><tr><