ogy.hl7.org/3.1.0/CodeSystem-v3-ReligiousAffiliation.html#v3-ReligiousAffiliation-1024\">1024</a></td><td>Jainism</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/3.1.0/CodeSystem-v3-ReligiousAffiliation.html#v3-ReligiousAffiliation-1025\">1025</a></td><td>Jehovah's Witnesses</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/3.1.0/CodeSystem-v3-ReligiousAffiliation.html#v3-ReligiousAffiliation-1026\">1026</a></td><td>Judaism</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/3.1.0/CodeSystem-v3-ReligiousAffiliation.html#v3-ReligiousAffiliation-1027\">1027</a></td><td>Latter Day Saints</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/3.1.0/CodeSystem-v3-ReligiousAffiliation.html#v3-ReligiousAffiliation-1028\">1028</a></td><td>Lutheran</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/3.1.0/CodeSystem-v3-ReligiousAffiliation.html#v3-ReligiousAffiliation-1029\">1029</a></td><td>Mahayana</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/3.1.0/CodeSystem-v3-ReligiousAffiliation.html#v3-ReligiousAffiliation-1030\">1030</a></td><td>Meditation</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/3.1.0/CodeSystem-v3-ReligiousAffiliation.html#v3-ReligiousAffiliation-1031\">1031</a></td><td>Messianic Judaism</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/3.1.0/CodeSystem-v3-ReligiousAffiliation.html#v3-ReligiousAffiliation-1073\">1073</a></td><td>Methodist</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/3.1.0/CodeSystem-v3-ReligiousAffiliation.html#v3-ReligiousAffiliation-1032\">1032</a></td><td>Mitraism</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/3.1.0/CodeSystem-v3-ReligiousAffiliation.html#v3-ReligiousAffiliation-1074\">1074</a></td><td>Native American</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/3.1.0/CodeSystem-v3-ReligiousAffiliation.html#v3-ReligiousAffiliation-1075\">1075</a></td><td>Nazarene</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/3.1.0/C